{"tid":1883783,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Rocket Punch胤卿創傷性滑膜炎！ 「全面暫停跳舞表演」年僅19歲","createTime":"2020-02-17T07:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T16:12:13.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"257f992e840f4ea93fe1a831153170fcae01c185","tid":1883783,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:50:50.000Z","msg":"Rocket Punch胤卿創傷性滑膜炎！ 「全面暫停跳舞表演」年僅19歲<br />\n<br />\n韓女團Rocket Punch出道於2019年，日前推出新歌《BOUNCY‬》回歸樂壇，沒想到其中19歲成員胤卿（윤경）17日起將暫停音樂節目的宣傳活動，等於未來的能見到她的場合瞬間少很多，讓粉絲相當心疼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4706/d4706457.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4706%2Fd4706457.jpg&h=3e74f222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Rocket Punch僅出道6個月。（圖／翻攝自Rocket Punch臉書）<br />\n<br />\nRocket Punch所屬經紀公司Woollim娛樂17日發出聲明：<br />\n<br />\n大家好，這裡是Woollim娛樂，首先感謝珍惜喜愛Rocket Punch的所有粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n在此公告Rocket Punch成員胤卿未來活動相關消息，胤卿準備新專輯的過程中感覺到膝蓋疼痛，送醫後被判斷為創傷性滑膜炎。<br />\n<br />\n遵從醫生的專業建議在之後的行程將減少胤卿的活動，為了藝人的狀態調整和成功的回歸進行了多方面的努力，在開始《BOUNCY‬》活動後進行觀察後，要消化在音樂節目所需的舞蹈表演是很困難的。<br />\n<br />\n不過，除了膝蓋以外整體狀態都沒有問題，成員本人不想讓已經等待6個月的粉絲太過擔心，會參與音樂節目外的所有活動與粉絲見面。<br />\n<br />\n因此，從本周音樂節目開始，《BOUNCY‬》將會由胤卿以外的5名成員帶來表演，胤卿會在恢復健康後再和成員們一起表演。<br />\n<br />\n再次感謝支持Rocket Punch第二張迷你專輯《RED PUNCH》的粉絲，我司將以藝人的健康作為第一要務並全力支持。<br />\n<br />\n也請大家繼續支持以5人形式帶來的《BOUNCY‬》表演。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4706/d4706458.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4706%2Fd4706458.jpg&h=e754e08e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲胤卿將不參與未來的音樂節目表演。（圖／翻攝自RCPC_members推特）<br />\n<br />\n牙純....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd771f2a94e14bccbdf76af6dd2717dfc6eaeb91","tid":1883783,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:52:07.000Z","msg":"以後得返五個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b04b4cba43725646b0ef56a91f57ea29a0fd1c","tid":1883783,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd771f2a94e14bccbdf76af6dd2717dfc6eaeb91","tid":1883783,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:52:07.000Z","msg":"以後得返五個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:52:55.000Z","msg":"吊...出道得半年變左金希澈"},{"pid":"d52f88f325763dd929cd2cce85ba571aade14780","tid":1883783,"uid":34071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:54:11.000Z","msg":"真係多謝傻尻拳唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb5b29e6669729bf7c6bd4f74d68c9cd8bd85fc","tid":1883783,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d52f88f325763dd929cd2cce85ba571aade14780","tid":1883783,"uid":34071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:54:11.000Z","msg":"真係多謝傻尻拳唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fedf1386bb3d0ae7148db892d24548246bcb79d8","tid":1883783,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:58:08.000Z","msg":"我買拳妹隻新碟就係中左佢張卡..😭"},{"pid":"4e403c860b6faab790eb47b46166b86ed08faeb2","tid":1883783,"uid":316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d52f88f325763dd929cd2cce85ba571aade14780","tid":1883783,"uid":34071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3